X,Y,Z
corr(X,Y)=-1
Var \ X\neq 0
X=0
Var \ X>0
 Var\left(\frac X{\sqrt{Var \ X}}+ \frac Y{\sqrt{Var\ Y}}\right) = 2 + 2corr(X,Y)=0 
 \frac X{\sqrt{Var \ X}} = - \frac Y{\sqrt{Var\ Y}} =  + \frac Z{\sqrt{Var\ Z}} = - \frac X{\sqrt{Var \ X}} 
\bigl(\begin{smallmatrix} 8 &-1&-1\\ -1 & 8&-1\\ -1&-1&8 \end{smallmatrix} \bigr)
>0
